Package: fmriarrow
Type: Package
Title: Fast, Spatially-Aware fMRI Data Access using Apache Arrow/Parquet
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An optimized fMRI data format using Apache Arrow/Parquet for fast, 
    spatially-aware time series access. Converts neuroim2 NeuroVec objects to 
    Z-order indexed Parquet files for efficient spatial querying without loading 
    entire 4D volumes into memory.
